title: Kiss Man Man Dark Skin Tone Medium Dark Skin Tone
description: Two men, one with dark skin tone and the other with medium-dark skin tone, kissing. Represents romantic affection between same-sex couples.
apple_vendor_description: On Apple devices, this emoji depicts two men sharing a tender kiss, with their skin tones rendered in a deep, rich dark and medium-dark hue, showcasing Apple's commitment to diverse representation. The characters are designed with soft, rounded edges and a subtle 3D effect, conveying warmth and affection through their gentle embrace. This visual expression of love and partnership is a beautiful addition to digital conversations, celebrating romantic connection.
